[08:35:30.153][VCOM] [uint8] PHR format: 0=misc IEEE802154 modulations, PHR 1byte
[08:35:30.158][VCOM] 1=SUN FSK, PHR 2bytes
[08:35:30.163][VCOM] 2=SUN OFDM, PHR 4bytes
[08:35:30.168][VCOM] 3=SUN OQPSK, PHR 4bytes
